name: preen tank
description:
The preen tank is made from a neoprene like material so even on a hanger it'll stand up for itself. And when it's surrounding a human body it kind of glides around. Whether you're neo to preening or preen to feel renewed, the preen tank gets it together for you.


size / one size stretch 
cotton-poly blend 
made in berlin 
Ships from nyc anywhere in the world

name: bronzed gremlin sweat shirt
description:
Sometimes, there's no monkey, there's a monster. Waiting to claw its way out of your mind. For those days, the bronzed gremlin sweat shirt acts as a talisman. Like a shot of whiskey that warms the chest even on the rainiest days. Won't say it's a lucky sweatshirt, but there's a reason the one third of the Irish flag is green. Find out for yourself... 


size / adult small 
cotton and silk panel
sweatshirt made mostly brooklyn
Ships anywhere in the world

name: blue hands sweat shirt
description:
Equal parts shiny and equal parts morose. Like a bright day and a popped blue balloon and a melted ice cream on the ground. Warm sunlight on a rainy day. The blue hands sweatshirt is for boys and girls alike who are looking to come out of the fog and turn on the headlights. 


size / adult medium
50% cotton & 50 % polyester
sweatshirt made in honduras and brooklyn
Ships anywhere in the world

name: asym top in lavender with zip
description:
The asym top comes in a subtle hue of lavender, the perfect shade for a meandering walk in the woods. Weather any weather, whether or not you wear the appropriate outerwear, with this wow-ing washed out lavender top. It has a unique texture--the stiffness of suede gives a sculptural shape to this vegetarian's delight. Slip it over your head, and venture out. The world awaits. The non functional zipper is an added bonus. The asym top is shown here accompanied by the beach dress and on its own. Dress is unfortunately not included.

Size: 34 / extra small 
Handmade in Berlin. Ships anywhere in the world.

name: asym top in cotton
description:
A breezy cotton top with a bubble hem to boot. The asym top in cotton also has beautiful detail work in tones of yellow, green, gold, lavender and red. 

Size: 36 / small 
Handmade in Berlin. Ships anywhere in the world
